---
title: Cheesy Mexican Smashed Chickpeas & Garlic Rice with Flaked Almonds & Pickled Onion Salsa
description: Don’t be fooled by the ‘smashed’ in our Mexican smashed chickpea bowl, this dish is tranquil and easy, perfect for
any hectic weekday night. Soothing rice soaks up an ensemble of tastes from the pickled onion, spiced chickpeas
and toasted pumpkin seeds. So don’t worry, you can sit back and relax into dinner tonight.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*We’ve replaced the pumpkin seeds in this recipe with flaked
almonds due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
